      <title>葡萄牙萨尔门托表示相信法国将解决危机</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/portugal-s-sarmento-says-he-s-confident-france-will-solve-crisis</link>
      <description><![CDATA[葡萄牙财政部长若阿金·米兰达·萨尔门托表示，法国当前的政治危机并不对整个欧洲构成威胁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-09/portugal-s-sarmento-says-he-s-confident-france-will-solve-crisis</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 10:01:03 GMT</pubDate>
